{"tid":1035257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遷粵養老　64歲婦失蹤　工聯會：同類個案多　半數未能尋回","createTime":"2019-02-24T13:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T05:24:28.000Z","uid":47714,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3648e316e9e44c55ce1e7af482738ce6b08c427a","tid":1035257,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150730/19237125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150730%2F19237125&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=67ab457e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150730%2F19237125&h=21ad4b7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150730/19237125</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is.gd/DJQtAN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FDJQtAN&h=dd4007ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東現有約3萬名養老港人，但求助機制不足令人憂慮。本報接獲港人求助，指在內地養老的64歲母親離奇失蹤近兩周，質疑公安未有積極援助。有協助內地港人的機構指類似事故非個別事件，專家則建議長者家人宜為在內地養老長者申請平安鐘、平安電話等服務，免長者失蹤時無從施救。<br />\n<br />\n失蹤的64歲港婦魏桂燕，7月17日在廣東茂名市失蹤後一直無音訊，入境處稱昨回覆指已向家屬了解事件，並會與駐粵經貿辦事處保持聯繫。入境處稱並沒有在內地失蹤香港長者的統計，但廣州工聯會諮詢服務中心的蕭先生稱，該中心每年都收到數宗港人在內地失蹤的求助個案，其中不少是長者，約一半未能尋回。"},{"pid":"55283800bbcdb71610c88dcf49a657f87b90872e","tid":1035257,"uid":77092,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09ac1072ae3ab817fb2b57142e128255d6fa8b15","tid":1035257,"uid":52946,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"返大陸養老姐係加速死亡"},{"pid":"c51a2f54fe4b2cfa2fb50bad0c51b921f2dd0907","tid":1035257,"uid":71676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"09ac1072ae3ab817fb2b57142e128255d6fa8b15","tid":1035257,"uid":52946,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"返大陸養老姐係加速死亡"},"cite